<plot>Ralph Staub takes his Columbia camera and Louella Parsons to the opening show of the annual Ice Capades in Hollywood, and lots of Hollywood people show up in their see-and-be-seen style. Among those seeing and seen are Guy Madison, Gail Russell, June Haver, Fred MacMurray, Rhonda Fleming, Jayne Mansfield, Ralph Edwards and Gary Cooper and his wife.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?243235</url></doc>
